pageContext.claim: “The Democrats will do anything to avoid a trial in the Senate in order to protect Sleepy Joe Biden, and expose the millions and millions of dollars that 'Where’s' Hunter, & possibly Joe, were paid by companies and countries for doing NOTHING. Joe wants no part of this mess!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats held onto the impeachment articles for four weeks in order to get more assurances on Senate procedures, not because they were afraid of which witnesses might be called to testify. They had been arguing for relevant witnesses.
